<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Ok, I see the dmg output is screwy post 50. I agree with Arkkada on one thing, and one thing only, you CAN control your pet, I have been in hate/fear I have NO prob controlling pets once we have broken the zone(but then again what raid party allows you to summon one before your on the ground?).  Enchies praise me all the time for my superior pet control, it CAN be done.  It is just alot harder without a pet no attack command.  One prob I want to se fixed is if we are elementalists...gimme my damn root! =P.<P>Now, if you dont know how to control your pet...let me explain.<P>When you hear the inc.. do the assist crap and pet attack, WATCH YOUR PET, if it turns away, and you here the mezzing tell by the enchie do a pet back off a million times until it is mezzed, it works for me.  While fighting one mob and there has been adds and you don't know if the pet has taunted off and is going to break mez, tell it to back off then re attack that simple command wipes hate list and will keep your pet in his place.  I have a ****ty pentium 233 and a 36.6k modem and I pull this off FINE.  <P>Pathing sucks, ya I agree, thats why you allow all the other classes to break things up without your pet, then when you get to the camp area, you summon.  I mean when you break a camp you all complain (yes I admit me too) about how your pet dmg/dd sux do you think then that it makes a difference if you just nuke?  And at lvl 54 we get a 2sec casting time/450dmg 175mana dd...that is insane, my friend Tykin has this one spell that is 650 dmg AE spell 2 sec casting time(the name escapes me at this moment) and almost killed 4 people in the arena when we were having fun.<P>Overall I think we need upgrades big time since I spend on average 2 hours asking for groups before I get one or become so discouraged I just log. We simply aren't needed in groups anymore, and I can't tell you how much I hate soloing.  This game has only 3 needs in a group Tank, Cleric, Enchie...thats all you ever need to kill anything and tank can include sk and pallie because they absorb dmg..Ranger..no comment =P.<P>Balancing in this game is a joke, a priest class at 55 (druid) out dd's us with the lvl 55 spell lol that seems kinda ridiculous to me.  I think with a few tweaks this class will be great, and I do still enjoy playing my mage not saying I hate him heh.<P>Razul Ar'Cane<BR>49th(and probably will be for a looonnggg time until I get my cpu upgraded =/)<BR>Erollisi Marr <Chain Of Honor>
